obaka&#8221;: il flamanco di Galvn si fonde con lIndia di Akram Khan\' href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2014/12/torobaka-il-flamanco-di-galvan-si-fonde-con-lindia-di-akram-khan/\' /><link rel=\'next\' title=\'Richard Strauss Celebrations: Le opere (&#8220;Capriccio&#8221;)\' href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/2014/12/richard-strauss-celebrations-le-opere-capriccio/\' /><meta name="generator" content="WordPress 4.5.3" /><link rel="canonical" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2014/12/verona-teatro-filarmonico-lucia-di-lammermoor-cast-alternativo/" /><link rel=\'shortlink\' href=\'http://www.gbopera.it/?p=78617\' /><link rel="alternate" type="application/json+oembed" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gbopera.it%2F2014%2F12%2Fverona-teatro-filarmonico-lucia-di-lammermoor-cast-alternativo%2F" /><link rel="alternate" type="text/xml+oembed" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-json/oembed/1.0/embed?url=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.gbopera.it%2F2014%2F12%2Fverona-teatro-filarmonico-lucia-di-lammermoor-cast-alternativo%2F&#038;format=xml" /><script type="text/javascript">function toggleLinkGrp(id){var e=document.getElementById(id);if(e.style.display==\'block\')e.style.display=\'none\';elsee.style.display=\'block\';}</script><link rel="stylesheet" href="http://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Carrois%20Gothic:300,400,400italic,700,700italic&amp;subset=latin,cyrillic-ext,cyrillic,latin-ext" type="text/css" /><style type="text/css">h1,h2,h3,h4,h5,h6{font-family:"Carrois Gothic",Arial,sans-serif}</style><link rel="shortcut icon" href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2014/05/favicon.ico"><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-76x76.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" sizes="76x76" /><link href="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/themes/wp-pravda/img/icons/apple-touch-icon-120x120.png" rel="apple-touch-icon" si